        "content": "<blockquote>\n<p>No formula of this sort is known that lets you compute individual decimal digits of π</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Seems like good evidence that decimal is a flawed base. <span aria-label=\"smile\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f642\" role=\"img\" title=\"smile\">:smile:</span></p>",
